Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.93,0:08:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Oguri Cap?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.23,0:08:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Tinggal 200 meter lagi!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.44,0:08:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Oguri Cap mendekat\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}dengan kecepatan tinggi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.27,0:08:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Ini pertarungan antara Umamusume abu-abu!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.69,0:08:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Sekarang lihat...\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}aku mengambil posisi pimpinan!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.61,0:08:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Oguri Cap tambah kecepatan lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.37,0:08:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Maju!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.91,0:08:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Oguri!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.33,0:08:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Dia menutup jarak!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.58,0:09:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Tiga langkah, tidak, dua langkah lagi!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Bisakah dia menyusul Tamamo Cross?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.09,0:09:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Tidak!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.55,0:09:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Dia tak bisa!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Tamamo Cross mengebut,\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}mempertahankan posisi memimpin!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.10,0:09:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Tamamo Cross, aku tahu kau berbeda!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.69,0:09:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Seolah aku akan membiarkanmu mendekat!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.02,0:09:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Aku hanya harus tetap memimpin dan...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.11,0:09:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Kakiku...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Ini keram...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Itu dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.96,0:09:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Dia mengebut dan melewati\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}furlong terakhir dalam waktu 11 detik.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Mustahil dia bisa terus begitu\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}setelah di posisi kedua sepanjang lomba.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.92,0:09:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Hanya satu langkah\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}antara Tamamo Cross dan Oguri Cap!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.22,0:09:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Apa Tamamo Cross sudah letih?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.47,0:09:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:10:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Sedikit lagi! Hanya satu milimeter lagi!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.06,0:10:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Sial! Garis finis terasa sangat jauh!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.40,0:10:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Aku tak bisa merasakan kakiku...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.82,0:10:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Lenganku mati rasa...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.44,0:10:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Bahkan paru-paruku rasanya mau meledak!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.74,0:10:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Apa ini? Apa aku sudah mencapai batasku?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.41,0:10:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Apa di sini kisahku berakhir?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku berhasil!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.25,0:10:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku satu detik lebih cepat\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}dari minggu lalu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Bukankah itu keren! Kerja bagus, Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku tahu kau mampu dan aku benar!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.97,0:10:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Trik mengayunkan lengan\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}yang kau ajarkan padaku sangat hebat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.06,0:10:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Rasanya seperti\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}aku menarik diriku ke depan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.35,0:10:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Lihat? Apa kubilang?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Gunakan lenganmu saat berlari\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}lebih sering dari yang kau kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.86,0:10:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Mengayun lengan membuatmu mengikuti irama\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}dan jaga pusat tubuh bagus dan seimbang.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:11:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Saat keadaan sulit, cukup ayunkan\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}lengan dan angkat kaki lebih tinggi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.54,0:11:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Ya, itu yang dikatakan di TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.33,0:11:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Jadi, TV adalah pelatihku?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.96,0:11:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kecerdasanmu juga menjadi lebih tajam!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Astaga, sudah cukup larut.\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Hampir waktunya kita...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.64,0:11:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kau tahu? Tidak usah dipikirkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Satu putaran lagi! Siapa tahu,\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}kali ini kau lebih cepat dua detik.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kau mau membuat keluargamu bangga, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.23,0:11:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Sebaiknya kita membuatmu bagus dan cepat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.90,0:11:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.99,0:11:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}- Kau tahu, Pak Tua?\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}- Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.57,0:11:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Suatu hari, aku akan menjadi sangat cepat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.74,0:11:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku memang berharap begitu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku akan menjadi sangat cepat\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}dan tak terhentikan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Aku akan menjadi yang terbaik di Jepang!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Pak Tua, apa kau menonton?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.76,0:11:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Kau lihat tanganku berayun?\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Itu semua berkat kau.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Saat keadaan sulit,\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}ayunkan saja lengan itu...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.39,0:12:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Lalu, angkat kaki lebih tinggi!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.44,0:12:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Sudah kubilang, 'kan?\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku akan jauh lebih cepat,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}membuat keluargaku bangga...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.11,0:12:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}dan menjadi yang terbaik di Jepang!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.75,0:12:35.25,tanda,,0,0,0,,PETIR PUTIH
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.34,0:12:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Selamat datang, Tamamo Cross,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.88,0:12:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}di Zone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.89,0:12:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Tamamo Cross melesat maju\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}dengan kecepatan kilat lagi!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Tinggal 100 meter lagi! Oguri Cap\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}hanya bisa menyaksikan badai mengamuk!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Tamamo Cross melesat\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}langsung menuju garis finis!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.57,0:12:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Gadis itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.36,0:13:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Apa-apaan? Kau pasti bercanda.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Mustahil mungkin dia punya lebih dari itu!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.75,0:13:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Angin, suara kaki balapan,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.08,0:13:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}bahkan sorakan kerumunan...\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Semuanya menjadi sunyi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.76,0:13:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Seolah aku di dunia ini sendirian...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.68,0:13:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Lihatlah fokus itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.14,0:13:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Pembalap yang menentukan eranya\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}pasti akan mencapai kondisi ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.77,0:13:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Di sana, mereka menemukan kekuatan\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}yang belum mereka tahu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.35,0:13:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}jauh melampaui batas\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}yang seharusnya mereka miliki.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.73,0:13:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Itu adalah Zone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.81,0:13:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Membawa kembali kenangan, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.57,0:13:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.53,0:13:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kelihatannya Tamamo Cross\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}sekarang salah satu dari kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.86,0:13:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Apa itu tadi?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.33,0:13:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Oguri!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.74,0:13:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Sudah selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.41,0:13:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Oguri mencapai batasnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.04,0:13:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}- Tapi dia pasti...\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}- Lihatlah dia...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:14:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Ini belum selesai!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.22,0:14:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Aku masih bisa...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.97,0:14:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Dia bahkan tak bisa berlari lurus.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.86,0:14:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Sampai saat itu, kami semua mengira\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}kami tahu apa yang akan terjadi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.94,0:14:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Binatang Buas mengamuk di ibu kota,\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}menumbangkan pembalap nasional papan atas.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.66,0:14:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Kami semua berasumsi Tamamo Cross\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}tak akan berbeda.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.08,0:14:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Tapi mungkin kami terlalu terburu-buru.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.88,0:14:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Dia benar-benar puncak balapan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.92,0:14:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Petir Putih, Tamamo Cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.73,0:15:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Itu balapannya!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.40,0:15:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Juara pertama Tamamo Cross,\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}pemenang pertempuran abu-abu kita!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.11,0:15:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Artinya, dia pembalap pertama yang menang\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}dua balapan Tenno Sho berturut-turut!{\i0}
