Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.28,0:15:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kau berhasil, Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.46,0:15:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Juara kedua adalah Oguri Cap!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.71,0:15:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Pelari depan Lord Royal\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}di posisi tiga teratas!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.13,0:15:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Sulit dipercaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Sprint terakhir Oguri Cap\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}tak diragukan salah satu yang terbaik.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.93,0:15:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Tapi bahkan setelah lari di baris kedua,\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Tamamo Cross menjaga...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.97,0:15:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Tidak, dia memperlebar keunggulannya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.27,0:15:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Siapa yang bisa bersaing\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}dengan kekuatan macam itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.19,0:15:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Bisakah siapa pun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.73,0:15:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku menang.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku berhasil. Aku menang!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.45,0:15:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Apa kau melihatnya, Pak Tua?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.83,0:15:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku yang terbaik di Jepang!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Oguri...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.47,0:16:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Akselerasi Tamamo di akhir... Apa itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.81,0:16:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Bagus mengetahuinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.69,0:16:27.61,tanda,,0,0,0,,PERTAMA - TAMAMO CROSS-KEDUA - OGURI CAP
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.70,0:16:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Mustahil...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.66,0:16:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Dia kalah? Oguri kalah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.45,0:16:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Ya, tapi... Lalu apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.04,0:16:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Dia tetap luar biasa! Ayolah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.41,0:16:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Norn...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.54,0:16:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Bahkan belum setahun sejak dia pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Dia menang enam balapan berturut-turut!\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Dapat juara kedua di G1!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.63,0:16:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Oguri luar biasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Ya, itu benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.18,0:16:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Tamamo Cross hari ini sangat kuat
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.98,0:17:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}tapi aku jamin, Oguri\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}yang mengeluarkan kekuatan itu darinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Dia tak perlu malu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.32,0:17:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Angkat kepalamu tinggi-tinggi, Oguri Cap.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Aku kalah...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.32,0:17:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Apa salahku?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.58,0:17:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Apa itu kecepatanku? Daya tahanku?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.20,0:17:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Apa aku terlalu lambat bereaksi?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.29,0:17:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Hei, Ogurin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Balapan yang bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.80,0:17:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Atau mungkin{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}aku hanya tak cukup menginginkannya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.93,0:17:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Meski kau mungkin sedih setelah kalah,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.44,0:17:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}tapi semangat juangmu masih tinggi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.73,0:17:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Sulit dipercaya itu terjadi lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.19,0:17:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kenapa selalu kau yang mendorongku maju?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.95,0:17:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Lupakan saja. Aku bicara pada diriku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.49,0:18:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku hanya mau bilang
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}kalau siapa pun pantas menjadi rivalku,\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}itu kau!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Mereka memang beruntung.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.21,0:18:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Ya. Persaingan yang luar biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.51,0:18:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Mulai sekarang,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}tak akan ada seorang pun yang bilang\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Umamusume abu-abu tak bisa balapan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Tidak peduli sesering apa itu terjadi,\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}kekalahan tak pernah terasa lebih pahit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.53,0:18:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Sial...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.86,0:18:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Baiklah, sebaiknya aku pergi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.91,0:18:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku harus siap-siap\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}untuk konser kemenangan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.91,0:18:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.37,0:18:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}"Tama"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.37,0:18:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Apa ini balasan untuk Ogurin sebelumnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku mau minta bantuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Bantuan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.84,0:18:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Lucu sekali. Aku baru\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}mau mengatakan hal yang sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.93,0:19:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Balapan lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Nanti aku akan mengalahkanmu lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.40,0:19:11.57,tanda,,0,0,0,,TERKONFIRMASI
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.15,0:19:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Jadi, ini Tamamo Cross...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.78,0:19:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Gunung yang jauh dan menjulang tinggi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.88,0:19:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Oguri pasti terlambat...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.63,0:19:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Ada apa? Apa dia membolos?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.09,0:19:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku yakin kekalahannya cukup mengejutkan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.64,0:19:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Bagaimanapun, ini kekalahan pertamanya\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}sejak datang ke ibu kota.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.52,0:19:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kalah juga berdampak buruk padanya, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.35,0:19:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Siapa sangka...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.40,0:19:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\i1}Cuma lari pagi...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.32,0:19:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Tunggu, kau baru balapan kemarin...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.62,0:20:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Bukankah seharusnya kau pemulihan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku tak punya waktu untuk itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.54,0:20:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Balapanku berikutnya sebentar lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.30,0:20:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Oguri!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.01,0:20:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kami siap mulai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.38,0:20:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Seperti biasa, mulai dengan\N{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}mengecek posturmu dan mulai berlari.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.85,0:20:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Baik!
